	copyright = {© 2015 The Authors Remote Sensing in Ecology and Conservation published by John Wiley \& Sons Ltd on behalf of Zoological Society of London., This is an open access article under the terms of the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial License, which permits use, distribution and reproduction in any medium, provided the original work is properly cited and is not used for commercial purposes.},
